ygData.subject: Re: EQ Patches Update
ygData.msgSnippet: Temple is up, along with ranger, cleric, pure caster and bard s armor quest. Shaman s was still bugged in test and might or might not be put in with this
ygData.messageBody:
Temple is up, along with ranger, cleric, pure caster and bard's armor quest. Shaman's was
still bugged in test and might or might not be put in with this patch.

Pure caster, bard and cleric quest is in temple of So, ranger one at Kit forest with that
guildmaster/mistress (Morin male ver give the armor quest, female ver gives the short
sword one), shaman is at either lake or one of the karana plains.
